    "outcome": "Outcome",
    "elEzabyProject": {
      "title": "Nationwide SD-WAN for El Ezaby Pharmacies",
      "tag": "Networking",
      "desc": "El Ezaby – Egypt’s #1 pharmacy network – partnered with Stackhubs to modernize connectivity across 450+ branches nationwide.",
      "summary": "El Ezaby - Egypt’s #1 pharmacy network - partnered with Stackhubs to modernize connectivity across 450+ branches in all governorates. We designed and delivered a nationwide SD-WAN (VMware VeloCloud) with high availability at the Data Center and HQ, then rolled out one edge per branch with tiered Internet redundancy (Platinum/Gold/Silver). The entire deployment was completed in 3 months, and Stackhubs now operates the platform as a 3-year managed service, ensuring performance, security, and 24/7 support.",
      "hero": "Modernizing pharmacy connectivity across Egypt with VMware SD-WAN.",
      "challenge": "El Ezaby needed a resilient, secure, and centrally managed network to support critical healthcare and retail applications (ERP, e-prescriptions, POS, inventory sync, and digital services) across hundreds of locations. The legacy model made branch turn-ups slow, visibility limited, and uptime dependent on single links in many sites.",
      "approach": "Stackhubs designed an SD-WAN architecture using VMware VeloCloud, delivering HA at the core (DC & HQ) and a standardized single-box footprint per branch. We introduced a tiered connectivity model(Platinum/Gold/Silver) so high-traffic or mission-critical locations receive more ISP diversity. Rollout followed a factory-style playbook: zero-touch provisioning, parallel site waves, and nightly cutovers — allowing the entire program to complete in three months.",
      "outcome": "The network gained intelligent path selection, application-aware QoS, and centralized policy control. Branches now enjoy higher uptime and consistent app performance; the operations team gained real-time visibility and faster troubleshooting. Stackhubs continues to run the solution as a managed service with proactive monitoring, SLAs, and continuous optimization.",
      "highlights": {
        "title": "Project at a Glance",
        "industry": "Retail Pharmacy / Healthcare",
        "scope": "DC + HQ + 450 branches (all Egyptian governorates)",
        "technology": "VMware VeloCloud SD-WAN",
        "availability": "DC (2 devices), HQ (2 devices), 1 edge per branch",
